<br/>
&quot;MAAP ALUULA TECH BAG COLLECTION<br/>
<br/>
Product highlight of this weekend is the @maap.cc @aluulacomposites Tech Bag Collection – a weatherproof everyday carry system built where cycling performance materials meet daily mobility. Merging aesthetics and performance into everyday carry, the collection introduces the Tech Tote, Tech Musette and Tech Pouch – designed for a life around bikes, from commuting and training to travel. Each piece is constructed with recycle-ready ALUULA Graflyte™ fabric and ultra-high-molecular-weight polyethylene (UHMWPE), delivering exceptional strength in an ultralight, water-resistant build. With a strength-to-weight ratio up to eight times that of steel, the material combines durability, waterproof protection and minimal weight, creating a streamlined carry system engineered to protect everyday essentials while handling the demands of daily movement on or off the bike.<br/>
<br/>
Available now via the brand’s website and MAAP stores.&quot;</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DWMw-LWDnbg/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
